WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:15.000
[Indoor laboratory setting. Presenter shown with paper towels and M-Fire AF31 product.]

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:35.000
[Presenter applies M-Fire AF31 liquid to one sheet of paper towel and sets it aside to dry.]

00:00:35.000 --> 00:01:05.000
[Time-lapse: 45 minutes pass as treated paper towel dries completely.]

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:25.000
[Presenter uses blowtorch on untreated paper towel. It ignites immediately and burns completely.]

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:50.000
[Presenter applies blowtorch to AF31-treated paper towel. The sheet does not ignite.]

00:01:50.000 --> 00:02:10.000
[Treated paper towel chars only at point of direct flame contact. No fire spreads.]

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:35.000
[Presenter uses flame to draw the letters "M" and "W" on the treated paper. The paper chars but does not catch fire.]

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:45.000
[Demonstration concludes. M-Fire AF31 logo and contact information displayed.]
